; Regression test for issue #1110: the convert command incorrectly handles the cost field (BZ#1110)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1110
;
; When converting a CSV with a commodity Amount column and a Cost column,
; the cost annotation (@@ $cost) should appear on the primary posting.
; Currently it is silently dropped, though the cost IS used for the
; balancing posting amount.

test -f /dev/null convert $sourcepath/test/input/1110.csv --input-date-format %Y/%m/%d -> 0
2014/01/01 * Broker
    Expenses:Unknown                         10 AAPL
    Equity:Unknown                          $-500.00
end test
